 * 1. Door swing arcs (curved lines showing door movement)
 *    - Requires: arc/curve primitives (Milestone 5)
 *    - Workaround: Just show door opening as rectangle
 * 
 * 2. Fixtures (toilet, sink, bathtub)
 *    - Requires: Component library with predefined fixtures
 *    - Workaround: Create as small rooms or wait for component system
 * 
 * 3. Exact measurements from image
 *    - Image doesn't show dimensions
 *    - Workaround: Estimated proportions visually
 * 
 * 4. Hatching/patterns for different room types
 *    - Requires: CSS pattern fills (can use inline CSS when implemented)
 *    - Workaround: Use background colors
